WEBVTT

00:00:03.379 --> 00:00:08.179
In Berlin, Professor Roland Hetzer at the German Heart Institute

00:00:08.179 --> 00:00:12.380
corrects a ventricular septal defect in a ten-month-old girl.

00:00:12.380 --> 00:00:20.260
In Yena, Professor Johannes Schela at Friedrich Schiller University Clinic

00:00:20.260 --> 00:00:22.260
performs a liver resection.

00:00:26.260 --> 00:00:30.260
In London, Peter Earnshaw, a fellow of the Royal College

00:00:30.260 --> 00:00:33.259
who practices at guys in St. Thomas hospitals,

00:00:33.259 --> 00:00:36.259
performs a total knee replacement.

00:00:36.259 --> 00:00:40.259
